    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/ceb83ed1a52cb45c6faec3460738eaf4.poster.avif?t=1744551256\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/ceb83ed1a52cb45c6faec3460738eaf4.webm?t=1744551256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/ceb83ed1a52cb45c6faec3460738eaf4.mp4?t=1744551256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/3ced2e9c6d79e993d1fbbb893a3d730a.avif?t=1744551256\" width=618 height=70 /></span><br>古老的特兰顿家族的诅咒使得年轻的苏珊小姐不得不离开，踏上致命的旅程。旅程中，她将会面对许多来自亡灵世界的居民，结交朋友，也遭遇敌人，并得到最重要的问题的答案——谁是杀害她整个家族的真正凶手。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/a5dcb593e8e6c2010989b3c381f4b84c.poster.avif?t=1744551256\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/a5dcb593e8e6c2010989b3c381f4b84c.webm?t=1744551256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/a5dcb593e8e6c2010989b3c381f4b84c.mp4?t=1744551256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/c74c575e2743cea6063e1f2fdb61801b.avif?t=1744551256\" width=618 height=70 /></span><br>一天，在特兰顿家族的古老城堡中，一对慈爱的父母生下了一个女儿。这个女孩名叫苏珊。<br>苏珊的父亲格林先生是一个极具魅力与影响力的人，他的妻女都十分爱他。然而，格林先生神秘去世了。<br>苏珊的母亲阿加莎女士，因丈夫的去世而悲痛不已。她无法忍受失去亲人的痛苦，像影子一样在城堡里徘徊游荡。<br>阿加莎身边的人不忍看她痛苦悲伤，决定把她嫁给一个正派人士。此人就是奥斯丁先生，他是一个十分沉着冷静的富翁。<br>生活似乎有所好转，继父成了一家之主，把寡妇阿加莎和小苏珊置于他的控制之下<br>不过，这样的平衡是短暂的。<br>仿佛有厄运一般的黑猫在行走，传播罪恶和诅咒……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/d2a5fa91df37059354a0b0c23c165c39.poster.avif?t=1744551256\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/d2a5fa91df37059354a0b0c23c165c39.webm?t=1744551256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/d2a5fa91df37059354a0b0c23c165c39.mp4?t=1744551256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197160/extras/815372cbe56bb3341c4098d2a7f49b97.avif?t=1744551256\" width=618 height=70 /></span><br>《秘密城堡》是一部美丽而令人着迷的视觉小说，内含大量有趣的任务、机制和谜题，如物品制作、库存、相机操控和3D角色操控。游戏中有常规谜题，即你必须将正确的物品相互连接起来；也有迷你游戏，即你必须以不同的方式思考。随着你的游戏进展，谜题和任务会更加复杂，解决它们不再像一开始那样容易。<br> <br> 游戏提供了一个教学关卡，引导玩家了解其所有机制。享受精美的画面与动画。使用游戏提供的所有工具来解决最困难的谜题和迷你游戏。<br><br>序言包括：<br>- 教程级别<br>- 2 个完整级别<br>- 额外的小游戏<br>- 5 个字符<br>- 10 个过场动画<br>- 25 个任务",
